RT Dovydas Vitkauskas
🇺🇸 Expected US Delegation accompanying President Trump to China includes Elon Musk, Tim Cook (ex Apple), David Solomon (Goldman Sachs), Larry Fink (Blackrock) and other business leaders.
Which of the expected complex discussion topics can realistically be advanced during the talks:
A) De-esclalating Iran crisis;
B) Normalising trade relationship;
C) Managing artificial intelligence risks;
D) Addressing regional security and 🇹🇼Taiwan;
E) Other?

